üîπ 20. ADD EMPLOYEE (FROM UI)

Fields used:

Name

Department

Email

Salary

Status

Auto-generated:

EMP-IT-001

üîπ 21. UPDATE EMPLOYEE STATUS

From Dashboard:

Active ‚Üí On Leave

On Leave ‚Üí Resigned (Discontinue)

üîπ 22. SQL VERIFICATION COMMANDS
SELECT * FROM employees;
SELECT * FROM employees WHERE status='Active';
SELECT * FROM employees WHERE status='On Leave';
SELECT * FROM employees WHERE status='Resigned';
UPDATE employees SET status='On Leave' WHERE emp_code='EMP-IT-001';
UPDATE employees SET status='Resigned' WHERE emp_code='EMP-IT-001';
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM employees;

üîπ 23. EXIT MYSQL
exit;
